#. <section class="sutta" id="sn13.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "1. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Dutiyasamuddasutta"
msgstr "8. The Ocean (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn13.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāsamuddo parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, "
"ṭhapetvā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose the water in the ocean dried up and evaporated except "
"for two or three drops."

msgctxt "sn13.8:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.8:1.4"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ "
"yāni vā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, or "
"the two or three drops left?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.8:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ mahāsamudde udakaṃ, yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ "
"pariyādiṇṇaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated is certainly "
"more."

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.2"
msgid "appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhāni."
msgstr "The two or three drops left are tiny."

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.3"
msgid ""
"Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ "
"upenti mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā "
"udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, it’s "
"not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.”"

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done "
"with is more …”"

msgctxt "sn13.8:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.8:2.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
